Package au.edu.rmit.agtgrp.apparate.jpathplan.entites

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AStarSearchNode Deprecated
    This class has been deprecated since version 0.2
    ComputedPlan
    The shortest path computed by any path planning algorithm.
    Edge
    An Edge interface is used to represent the information related to transition between the states.
    Plan
    This is an interface which defines the basic requriements of the path returned by any path planning algorithm such that the client application can easily extract the information in the format it understands.
    SearchDomain
    A SearchDomain interface represents the search space graph as an abstract view of the environment/domain.
    SearchNode
    This class is a wrapper around Node interface, which stores useful annotations and parent pointers.
    State
    A Node interface is used to represent the states within the SearchDomain in a uniform way.
